Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Izumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, KT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the special couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan Broadcasting System is having a special 5-hour program...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Popular music producer, Takatou Kenzi, a.k.a. TK, proposes on the radio show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's so flashy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would we expect from a popular producer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so fast to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan, have you kissed him yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Matsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty funny, Massan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad for you too, Izumi-chan, for finding a permanent job,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though I'm a bit sad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such merry news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san, give her a happy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrants! Congrants! Congrants!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good  for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.17,0:02:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, sorry about the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something horrible about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a robot, but an android.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Studio One.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san, it's Isozaki-san from public relations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's airtime soon, so I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 24...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life advice program, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:21.07,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukie-chan! Don't die now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:24.24,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so sincere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.57,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you even say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.99,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,After her repeated battles against the Ora-ora Aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:27.83,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukie-chan's Nanyo-syndrome got worce,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.95,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,and she'll lose all of the liquid in her body within a few hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:32.33,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,But what could I have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:37.46,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice cap from the North Pole has covered the Northern Hemisphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.17,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Western Nations are almost completely destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:42.30,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukie-chan is our last hope to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:43.93,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:45.76,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen with the drama after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.22,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a miraculous turnabout in the story. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.52,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny is something we create with our own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.52,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, Yukie-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukie-chan's mother comes back from the 23rd century.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:52.98,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shake her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.44,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it shining?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is her mother coming from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:59.07,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to Yukie-chan next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so picky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.90,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,To be continued...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Kacchin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.45,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Story, planning, script, editing - Suga-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he took a day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's being followed by someone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.16,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Music - Arimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not something you should say with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.41,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer - Matsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.95,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,SFX - Ume-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the tape is near the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.21,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Starring Maico as Yukie-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san, the tape is ending soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.04,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiminobu-san as Kiminobu-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san, give me the S-21 jingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:20.55,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Ijuin-san as Ijuin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:21.88,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap it up with the drama synopsis, then we'll go to the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Yukie-chan S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Yukie-chan be able to save the Earth from destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look forward to the next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the next corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's Life Advice Against Your Will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will call a number randomly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and try to give advice for whatever problems the recipient may have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last week, nobody answered even after 20 calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try to advice people on their problems this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start the tel-tel-call!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if someone will answer this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On to the next tel-tel-call.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an android radio personality for Japan Broadcasting System, Maico.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is very sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but would you share a life problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wiil use the enormous amount of data I carry as an android to solve your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really radio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Your voice is being broadcasted nationally over the radio waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sudden! I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but let me hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you at least answer one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you suffering from anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any anxieties?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's not going well, or something that you are troubled about. Is there anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 10 years since I started living separately from my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man is your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's normal except for his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... he works for a mass media company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to come home in the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since around the time our daughter was born, he quit coming home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept himself busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even got himself involved with projects not assigned to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while leaving the family alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I asked him to watch after our sick daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he just read one letter, and headed back to his job, leaving her behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter nearly had pneumonia by the time I got back to her. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.66,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, if I didn't get back, that listener would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or just the other day, he disregarded te monthly day they've set up to meet with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me that she waited at a restaurant for him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wouldn't even keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.76,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was storming that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still troubling you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just said that you hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there should be no need to be troubled if you really hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you ask such a question to a woman approaching 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of my husband, who can be so caring to a total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no excuse to leave his family behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you mentioned that to your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted him to notice my feelings and our daughter's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only an android, so I cannot comprehend people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that I've learned after working as a personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, there are things that cannot be communicated unless you verbally say them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell your husband what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! I'm sure he'll catch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try, try, and try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to think a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hold on to such troubles for 10 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are truly amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that she truly loves her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she can talk with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back after these messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, that stings so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Maico-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did I make any mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as you told me before, I thought hard in my own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you can't lie the other day, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.74,0:09:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Maico?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san, did you just say Maico?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of cource.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an android after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are sincere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cheap program could still solve a 10-year-old problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I can't quit the radio biz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Isozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the life advice program,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cancel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you just listening to the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the worst bunch of junk imaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm the only man who can manage this bunch of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Densuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ume-san, let's go out for a drink someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-chan, would you stay with this program even after you get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga, give us good scripts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke, don't goof up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.20,0:10:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.82,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got this all the way out in Tibet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so nice, Kacchin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of cource.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family will finally be happy with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, I'll make Yukie-chan's dad the boss of the villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga, we're already off the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san told us that he falls into a slump unless he sees people's unhappiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have that in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just surpassed the script for Live from the South Pole Crossing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly a legendary script!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's super shining!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Suga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.57,0:12:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Densuke! Get an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:08.00,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Maico's Diary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the A.D., Densuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went out for a drink yesterday with the staff members.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, a store worker came over to me and handed me a piece of yellow paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:24.94,COMME,,0000,0000,0000,,Suga-san fainted unconscious. Matsu-san, Izumi-san, Ume-san, Kacchin-san, Densuke-san, they all ran for him. As for me... I could only just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said free beer ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been treated so well by a total stranger before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I'll go back to Bar Mugendai again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Android Ana Maico 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:29.91,LEFT,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pack of vampire bats are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
